 FTP issue is because when you set up name-based FTP services IIS7 wants the site name defined with the username so that IIS7 can associate the username with the site they wish to log in to.

Solution A
If you want more than one FTP site on your VPS you will need to :

Configure all FTP clients such that :
Host: Your IP
User: yourdomain.com|Username

Note the "|" that separates the Sitename and the Username.
